              <h1 class="page-title"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">A very old problem turns 30!</span>
</h1>
            
              
                      <a href="/content/list-by-author/Marianne+Freiberger">Marianne Freiberger</a> and             <a href="/content/list-by-author/Rachel+Thomas">Rachel Thomas</a>                <a class="plus-share-button" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Share this page!"
